		{
			dependencies: ["4BDE217F95FD62A2"]
			description: [
				"## <grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Overview</grad>"
				"The <grad from=#A800A8 to=#A800A8><pulse base=0.5 a=1.0 f=1.5>Stegonaut</pulse></grad> is a heavily armored defensive dragon species known for its exceptional protective instincts, social imprinting behavior, and battlefield resilience."
				"[gap=5]"
				"---"
				"[gap=5]"
				"<grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Their egg cannot be found.</grad>"
				"[gap=5]"
				"<grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>They can be found in the following biomes:</grad>"
				"[gap=0]"
				"&2Lush Caves&r"
				"[gap=5]"
				"---"
				"[gap=5]"
				"<grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Go to the next page to look how to tame them.</grad>"
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"## <grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Taming</grad>"
				"&6Required food&r"
				"Raw Cod, Raw Salmon, Hearty Dragon Meal."
				"Because they're social and bond easily, taming them is more about earning trust than controlling aggression."
				"<grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Go to the next page to view how to breed them.</grad>"
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"## <grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Breeding</grad>"
				"Requires a pair of one male and one female with full health. Shift + Right-click with the appropriate food item under the Taming section to initiate breeding. Should you breed one male dragon that you own with a female dragon that someone else owns, or otherwise, the baby will default to following the female."
				"<grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Go to the next page to view their abilities.</grad>"
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"## <grad from=#FFD700 to=#FFFF99 f=0.5>Keys - Abilities</grad>"
				"&eThis dragon has the ability to jump like vanilla Horses.&r"
				"&2Left-click&r: Bite."
				"&2X&r to switch to Chin Slamming"
				"&2Holding G&r: Swallow block and shoots"
				"&2Holding H&r: Does a slam that knocks entities back, and if you &2keep holding H&r, it'll perform a second slam, even stronger than the first one, to summon Amethyst pillars and also dealing damage and knocking things back "
			]
			id: "0F60F8C2EC30E677"
			min_width: 250
			shape: "none"
			size: 1.1d
			subtitle: "<typewriter><shadow><grad from=#D400D4 to=#D400D4 f=0.3>Terrible looking dragon.</grad></shadow>"
			tasks: [{
				id: "286DF42942651032"
